The games license is described in COPYING

Installation instructions can be found in INSTALL

A description of how to play the game can be found in MANUAL.

To get notified of new releases you can go to http://freshmeat.net/projects/wesnoth and 'subscribe to new releases'

Wesnoth User and Developer Forums can be found at http://forum.wesnoth.org

Some user created campaigns can be found under 'UserScenarios' at http://wiki.wesnoth.org

For more information, visit the official Battle for Wesnoth web site: http://www.wesnoth.org

